        <item>
            <title>iPhone FineWoven 保護套被外媒批評，容易褪色甩皮狀況如爛香蕉</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 08:58:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[手機配件]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[FineWoven]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iPhone 15]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221662</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>Apple 推出 iPhone 15 之時順勢停產皮革手機殼，改為推出新的 FineWoven 手機殼，成為新一代對應 MagSafe 充電的機殼選擇。近日外媒《Wall Street Journal》記者 Joanna Stern 就在 X （前稱 Twitter）分享其使用了 5 個月的 FineWoven 保護殼，圖片可見該保護殼除了滿布花痕及出現褪色問題外，更有明顯甩皮問題。Joanna Stern 的帖文引來不少 iPhone FineWoven 保護殼「苦主」留言，表示自己的手機殼也有同樣問題。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Here it is. My iPhone 15 Pro Max’s FineWoven case. Peeling edges, scratches and browning like a rotten banana.</p><p>An Apple spokesman said that the company’s cases are engineered at the highest standard to protect iPhones.  </p><p>More on this not-so-fine FineWoven case in my newsletter… <a href="https://t.co/cpDc46LpN8">pic.twitter.com/cpDc46LpN8</a></p><p>&mdash; Joanna Stern (@JoannaStern) <a href="https://twitter.com/JoannaStern/status/1761072266639458745?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 23, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>有網民表示，其 iPhone FineWoven 保護殼褪色情況非常嚴重，甚至使其 MagSafe Duo 充電座亦染上了保護殼的顏色。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221664" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447-456x580.jpg" alt="" width="456" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447-456x580.jpg 456w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227154447.jpg 707w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 456px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/Javi_J/status/1761128853223723035">Javi_J@X</a></p><p>網友 @CalumRaasay 表示自己去年 10 月才剛開始使用 FineWoven 手機保護殼，僅僅 4 個月其保護殼就如「戰損版」般，邊角位嚴重甩皮，而且保護殼背部花痕密佈。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1221666" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109-694x468.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="468" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109-694x468.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/20240227155109.jpg 751w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/CalumRaasay/status/1761112842382500230">CalumRaasay@X</a></p><p>@srcshelton 亦在 X 分享自己的 FineWoven 保護殼，表示「這是 Apple 發布過最差的產品，Apple 應該全額退款回收這個保護殼，並向用戶道歉」。</p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">The appalling state of an <a href="https://twitter.com/Apple?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">@Apple</a> 「FineWoven」 (e.g. real leather substitute) premium iPhone Pro case after only 4 months of standard real-world use: this product is the worst Apple has even released &#8211; it should be withdrawn and customers should receive a fully refund &amp; apology. <a href="https://t.co/WnyFN2HhPk">pic.twitter.com/WnyFN2HhPk</a></p><p>&mdash; Stuart Shelton (@srcshelton) <a href="https://twitter.com/srcshelton/status/1756331787926544663?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 10, 2024</a></p></blockquote><p><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div><p>資料來源：<a href="https://twitter.com/JoannaStern/status/1761072266639458745">JoannaStern@X</a>、<a href="https://www.businessinsider.com/people-are-dragging-apples-finewoven-cases-2024-2">Business Insider</a>、<a href="https://www.techradar.com/phones/some-iphone-15-owners-are-branding-apples-new-finewoven-case-its-worst-ever-product">Tech Radar</a>、<a href="https://www.cnbeta.com.tw/articles/tech/1420955.htm">cnBeta</a><br /><b>相關文章:</b></p><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/24/ios-17-3-special-features/mobile-phone/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iOS 17.3 必學功能　防盜竊 iPhone 保護 + 簡單查所有 Apple 產品保養</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/12/01/ios-17-senior-mode/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】iOS 17 老人模式快速設定，超大字簡約介面不怕撳錯掣</a></li><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/28/apple-car-plan-ends/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple 電動車計劃壽終正寢   2,000 名員工受影響</a></li></blockquote><p></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/iphone-finewoven-peel-like-banana/mobile-phone/phone-parts/">iPhone FineWoven 保護套被外媒批評，容易褪色甩皮狀況如爛香蕉</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
