        <item>
            <title>NVIDIA 黃仁勳：小孩不應學寫程式，學懂如何用 AI 更重要</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Oscar]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Tue, 27 Feb 2024 07:00:59 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[人工智能]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[AI]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NVIDIA]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黃仁勳]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1221490</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>最近 NVIDIA 行政總裁黃仁勳公開表示，現代小朋友不需要再學習編寫程式，反而應該專注發展其他領域並成為該領域的專家，再交由 AI 解決各式各樣的問題。</p><p><div class="video-container"><blockquote class="twitter-tweet" data-width="500" data-dnt="true"><p lang="en" dir="ltr">Jensen Huang, CEO of Nvidia, argues that we should stop saying kids should learn to code. <br><br>He argues the rise of AI means we can replace programming languages with human language prompts thus enabling everyone to be a programmer. <br><br>AI will kill coding.<a href="https://t.co/SxK9twhEby">pic.twitter.com/SxK9twhEby</a></p>&mdash; Dare Obasanjo🐀 (@Carnage4Life) <a href="https://twitter.com/Carnage4Life/status/1761483377365152234?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw">February 24, 2024</a></blockquote><script async src="https://platform.twitter.com/widgets.js" charset="utf-8"></script></div></p><p>日前黃仁勳出席於杜拜舉行的世界政府高峯會時提及其對編程的意見。黃仁勳認為， AI 發展迅速，現在編程重要性已不如以往。黃仁勳認為，即使 AI 目前仍然屬初期發展階段，編程也不再是重要技能。黃仁勳指，AI 發展日益蓬勃，人類可以專注在更有價值的專業知識，如生物學、教育、製造或農業等，編程可以交由 AI 處理。</p><p>黃仁勳表示，過去 10-15 年來，大部份科技巨頭都認為年輕人學習電腦科技及編寫程式等技術攸關重要，但在 AI 日新月異的成長下，年輕人已經不再需要學習這些技能。黃仁勳又表示他的工作就是為了創造一個人類不用學習寫程式的世界，AI 發展完善的情況下，全世界任何人也可以是程式設計員。</p><p>資料來源：<a href="https://www.techradar.com/pro/nvidia-ceo-predicts-the-death-of-coding-jensen-huang-says-ai-will-do-the-work-so-kids-dont-need-to-learn">Tech Radar Pro</a>、<a href="https://www.tomshardware.com/tech-industry/artificial-intelligence/jensen-huang-advises-against-learning-to-code-leave-it-up-to-ai">Tom&#8217;s Hardware</a></p><br /><b>相關文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/31/nvidia-geforce-rtx-4070-ti-super-review/game-channel/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【評測】NVIDIA RTX 4070 Ti SUPER    遊戲效能快 20% + 輕鬆超越上代旗艦</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/rtx-video-hdr/notebook/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【教學】任何 SDR 影片升級 HDR 實戰    NVIDIA RTX Video HDR 適用於全部 RTX 顯示卡</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/24/nvidia-rtx-4070-ti-super-unboxing/parts/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">【開箱】NVIDIA RTX 4070 Ti SUPER 顯示卡  16GB RAM 升級版夠抵玩</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/02/27/nvidia-ceo-no-need-to-learn-coding-anybody-can-be-a-programmer-with-technology/ai/">NVIDIA 黃仁勳：小孩不應學寫程式，學懂如何用 AI 更重要</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
